projects.description:
Flavourspace is a digital platform for food discovery and inspiration (B2B/B2C). 

- improvise with recipes online: replace individual ingredients and arrive at your perfect dish before stepping into the kitchen;

- explore food relationships: see similar dishes connected together in a single view; recipe search results do not have to be explored one by one anymore, but are shown within a network;

- get surprised: let our ultimate fusion engine automatically generate exotic or novel ingredient combinations for you.

